thread.title: Not everything is as it seems.
thread.title_full: Not everything is as it seems. - Review of BEST WESTERN PLUS El Rancho Inn, Millbrae, CA - TripAdvisor

author: Madeline D
title: Not everything is as it seems.
text: The beds and rooms are comfortable. Do not be dependent on shuttle service. They need at least an hour round trip even though it's close to the airport. They stop at 3 hotels. Also failed to send me check out receipts or anything. Not worth $200.00 for one night stay.
